<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>RHEIDOL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa, Na thu hi a lul pen,
 Khawvel sum chengcheng sangin;
 Lalpa na thu hih a hawih pen,
 Khawvel lopina sangin;
 Khuoizu sangin thum zaw'i,
 Ka lunggil a sukipak.

[V2]
 2. Gamthip, gamgaw hawh pai dingin,
 Na thu hin ei pui zelin;
 Ziehi &quot;Meipi vak&quot; chuh ahi,
 Israel chate'n a zuih kha;
 Eihaw ei pui dingin,
 A vakna a tuoi diek puoi.

[V3]
 3. Khawvel tuisuohgiet lien a hin,
 Lauthawng a ka len lai hin;
 Mal Aksi guolin Na thu hin,
 Ka van lampiu ei hilh hen;
 Chun, hun zui pai ta'ngkau,
 Kumsawt a mang talo din.

[V4]
 4. Thepna tuilien, thepna gal lien,
 Khawvel tawh ei do mahleh;
 Lalpa, ei vanin, Na thu chun,
 Thagau chemzam ahi ie;
 Lau puong kau Setan chuh,
 Nangmah hatna masawn in.</lyrics>
